dct_title_s: Chart showing Mr. Leigh Smith's track to Franz Josef Land and boat journey to Novaya Zemlya in 1881-1882
dct_description_sm: Outward track in the Eira and homeward track in boats shown in red. Sir Allen Young's track in the Hope shown in black. Dates of travel marked along routes. Sites of loss of Eira and abandonment of Austrian ship Tegetthoff are shown. Relief shown by hachures. From: Proceedings of the Royal Geographical Society and monthly record of geography. Vol. 5 (1883), no. 4, pp. 204-28; held in Firestone Library. Call number: G7 .J6873
